OL,3,CKiller jailed for an extra 13 years
OL,4,Cafter admitting to attempted murder
OL,6,FA convicted murderer from Hull has
OL,7,Fbeen sentenced for an extra 13 years
OL,8,Fafter admitting trying to kill two
OL,9,Fother inmates in top security prisons.
OL,11,FDuncan Heaton, 53, admitted attempting
OL,12,Fto murder David Minto at HMP Wakefield
OL,13,Fin October 2025, and Andong Abong Ashu
OL,14,Fat HMP Full Sutton, near York, in May
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FHeaton pleaded guilty to both charges.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
