PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1778767870
OL,3,CKiller jailed for an extra 13 years
OL,4,Cafter admitting to attempted murder
OL,6,FHeaton is already serving a life
OL,7,Fsentence with a minimum term of 21
OL,8,Fyears and six months for the murder of
OL,9,FKeith Opray in Hull in 2014.
OL,11,FAccording to reports of his sentencing
OL,12,Fat Hull Crown Court, disabled Mr Opray
OL,13,Fsuffered 43 stab wounds to his head,
OL,14,Fneck and body when he was attacked by
OL,15,Fthe defendant, who was a heroin addict.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
