PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1778767870
OL,3,CKiller jailed for an extra 13 years
OL,4,Cafter admitting to attempted murder
OL,6,FThe judge said the defendant will be
OL,7,Fin his 70s before he can be considered
OL,8,Ffor release, and added: "Whether you
OL,9,Fare ever safe to be released, well
OL,10,Fthat will be a matter for the Parole
OL,11,FBoard."
OL,13,F"They feel they have nothing to lose"
OL,15,FBen Leapman, editor of Inside Time,
OL,16,Fthe national prison newspaper, said
OL,17,Flast year there were nine homicides -
OL,18,Fa record high - in prisons in England
OL,19,Fand Wales.
OL,26,@pD@YOUsD@GO]uD@AOUuD@eO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
