PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1778767870
OL,3,CKiller jailed for an extra 13 years
OL,4,Cafter admitting to attempted murder
OL,6,FHe said: "It's dangerous to work in
OL,7,Fand it's dangerous to live in for
OL,8,Fprisoners.
OL,10,F"There's a particular issue in high
OL,11,Fsecurity prisons. With sentences
OL,12,Fgetting longer and longer, there are
OL,13,Fpeople in there serving 20 years, 30
OL,14,Fyears, 40 years before they're going
OL,15,Fto get out and they feel they have
OL,16,Fnothing to lose by attacking somebody.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1778767870
OL,3,CKiller jailed for an extra 13 years
OL,4,Cafter admitting to attempted murder
OL,6,F"Potentially they will attack a high
OL,7,Fprofile inmate because they feel they
OL,8,Fcan feel they can get some kind of
OL,9,Fkudos from doing that, and that's a
OL,10,Freal worry."
OL,12,FInside Time receives letters every
OL,13,Fmonth from serving prisoners.
OL,15,F"A lot of prisoners isolate in their
OL,16,Fcells because they're frightened to
OL,17,Fcome out."
OL,19,FOne worry Mr Leapman raised is that
OL,20,Factivities and education for prisoners
OL,21,Fhas reduced due to staff shortages.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]wD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
