PN,36609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1778767870
OL,3,CKiller jailed for an extra 13 years
OL,4,Cafter admitting to attempted murder
OL,6,F"I think if prisoners have something
OL,7,Fworthwhile to do and feel they're
OL,8,Fmaking progress, then they're less
OL,9,Flikely to be attacking one another."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
